tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center">Bloggy</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.anarieldesign.com/themes/blogging-wordpress-theme/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493" alt="ekho" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/bloggy.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>“Bloggy” WP theme is made for bloggers that need a simple yet effective tool to bring their thoughts to the world.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.anarieldesign.com/themes/blog-wordpress-theme/" target="_blank">Purchase Bloggy theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center">Passenger</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.anarieldesign.com/themes/travelers-wordpress-theme/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493" alt="ekho" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/passenger.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Passenger is the theme for travelers. It is modern, clean and responsive WordPress theme with some cool features every traveler needs. It is an easy to use theme with responsive layout that looks great on any device, big or small. It is compatible with Major Browsers, Smartphones and Tablet’s.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.anarieldesign.com/themes/travelers-wordpress-theme/">Purchase Passenger</a>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center">Grideon</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/grideon-responsive-creative-wordpress-theme/8002104?WT.ac=portfolio_item&amp;WT.z_author=ZERGE"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493" alt="ekho" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/grideon.png" width="590" height="30